text = "Welcome to My Demo Level!!
Make sure that when creating levels to follow the struct of the Scene Tree. I.E.
Node holds the whole group together. TopCanvas is for UI elements we don't want distorted by Shaders. SecondCanvas is for \"CameraFilters\". The player exists outside of the \"Level.\" In theory, on level change, we would just need to load the next level but keep the player in the scene tree.
"
